quote.summary: Chongqing Hongjiu Fruit Co Ltd is a China-based company mainly focused on managing the entire supply chain for quality fruits primarily grown in the places of origin of the world. The Company delivers fresh fruit products from local orchards to national retail terminals through sales and distribution network and end-to-end supply chain system. The Company operates the Hongjiu Fruit brand, including several sub brands. The Company owns rich product portfolio covering over 49 fruit categories, selecting and sourcing fruits from over 100 places of origin of the world for consumers. The Company's six core fruit products comprise durian, dragon fruit, longan, grapes, cherry and mangosteen. The company's other fruit categories mainly include citrus, apple, kiwi and mango. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the China market markets.
